---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer id="kontak" class="bg-[var(--dark)]">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[var(--dark)] py-16 sm:py-20">
    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-16 top-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]/14 blur-3xl"></span>
    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 bottom-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]/10 blur-3xl"></span>
    <div class="container-shell relative z-10 grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.95fr)_minmax(0,1.05fr)]">
      <img
        src="https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/23/2d/ca/80/warunk-wow-kwb-batu.jpg"
        alt="Area Warunk WOW KWB Batu"
        width="900"
        height="640"
        class="mx-auto h-64 w-full max-w-[28rem] rounded-3xl border border-[var(--accent)]/30 object-cover drop-shadow-[0_28px_38px_rgba(30,0,0,0.45)] sm:h-72"
        onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/images/logo-wow-kwb.jpg';this.classList.remove('object-cover');this.classList.add('object-contain');"
      />
      <div>
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Hassle-free coffee delivery</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl text-white sm:text-5xl">
          Everything Gets Better
          <br />
          With Coffee
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-sm text-white/86 sm:text-base">
          Nikmati kopi dan makanan favorit dengan pelayanan cepat, rasa konsisten,
          dan suasana kafe yang siap menemani aktivitas dari pagi sampai malam.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] px-5 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-black transition hover:bg-[var(--accent-strong)] sm:text-sm"
            href="https://www.instagram.com/warunk_wow_kwb/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Buka Instagram
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[var(--accent)]/75 px-5 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--accent)] transition hover:bg-[var(--accent)]/14 sm:text-sm"
            href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Warunk+WOW+KWB+Batu+Jl+Panglima+Sudirman+No.39"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Lihat Lokasi
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container-shell py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base text-white">Warunk WOW KWB</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/72">
          Coffee shop 24 jam dengan rooftop, live music, dan pilihan menu modern.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base text-white">Useful Links</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/72">
          <li><a class="transition hover:text-[var(--accent)]" href="#beranda">Home</a></li>
          <li><a class="transition hover:text-[var(--accent)]" href="#tentang">About Us</a></li>
          <li><a class="transition hover:text-[var(--accent)]" href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
          <li><a class="transition hover:text-[var(--accent)]" href="#testimoni">Reviews</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base text-white">Contact</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/72">
          Jl. Panglima Sudirman No.39, Kota Batu, Jawa Timur
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/72">Open: 24 Jam</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/72">Reservasi: 0812-3223-9999</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base text-white">Social Media</h3>
        <a
          class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-black transition hover:bg-[var(--accent-strong)]"
          href="https://www.instagram.com/warunk_wow_kwb/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Follow Instagram
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10 border-t border-[var(--accent)]/24 pt-5 text-center text-xs text-white/55">
      &copy; {currentYear} Warunk WOW KWB. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
